#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using LINSTOR Without DRBD"
msgstr "DRBDを使わないLINSTOR"

#. type: delimited block -
msgid "LINSTOR can be used without DRBD as well. Without DRBD, LINSTOR is able to provision volumes from LVM and ZFS backed storage pools, and create those volumes on individual nodes in your LINSTOR cluster."
msgstr "LINSTORはDRBDを使わずとも使用できます。 DRBDがなくても、LINSTORはLVMおよびZFS 下位ストレージプールからボリュームをプロビジョニングし、LINSTORクラスタ内の個々のノードにそれらのボリュームを作成できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
msgid "Currently LINSTOR supports the creation of LVM and ZFS volumes with the option of layering some combinations of LUKS, DRBD, or NVMe-oF/NVMe-TCP on top of those volumes."
msgstr "現在LINSTORはLVMとZFSボリュームの作成をサポートしており、LUKS、DRBD、または NVMe-oF/NVMe-TCP の組み合わせをそれらのボリュームの上に重ねることもできます。"

#. type: delimited block -
msgid "For example, assume you have a Thin LVM backed storage pool defined in your LINSTOR cluster named, `thin-lvm`:"
msgstr "例えば、LINSTORクラスターで定義されたThin LVMをバックエンドストレージプールとして持っていると仮定します。このストレージプールの名前は `thin-lvm` です。"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor --no-utf8 storage-pool list\n"
"+--------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
"| StoragePool | Node      | Driver   | PoolName          | ... |\n"
"|--------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-a | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-b | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-c | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-d | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"+--------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor --no-utf8 storage-pool list\n"
"+--------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
"| StoragePool | Node      | Driver   | PoolName          | ... |\n"
"|--------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-a | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-b | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-c | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"| thin-lvm    | linstor-d | LVM_THIN | drbdpool/thinpool | ... |\n"
"+--------------------------------------------------------------+\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You could use LINSTOR to create a Thin LVM on `linstor-d` that's 100GiB in size using the\n"
"following commands:\n"
msgstr "次のコマンドを使用して、`linstor-d` 上に100GiBのThin LVMを作成するには、LINSTORを使用できます：\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-definition create rsc-1\n"
"# linstor volume-definition create rsc-1 100GiB\n"
"# linstor resource create --layer-list storage \\\n"
"          --storage-pool thin-lvm linstor-d rsc-1\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-definition create rsc-1\n"
"# linstor volume-definition create rsc-1 100GiB\n"
"# linstor resource create --layer-list storage \\\n"
"          --storage-pool thin-lvm linstor-d rsc-1\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You should then see you have a new Thin LVM on `linstor-d`. You can extract the device path from\n"
"LINSTOR by listing your linstor resources with the `--machine-readable` flag set:\n"
msgstr "その後、`linstor-d` に新しい Thin LVM が作成されていることが確認できるはずです。LINSTOR からデバイスパスを抽出するには、`--machine-readable` フラグを設定して linstor リソースをリストアップしてください。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor --machine-readable resource list | grep device_path\n"
"            \"device_path\": \"/dev/drbdpool/rsc-1_00000\",\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor --machine-readable resource list | grep device_path\n"
"            \"device_path\": \"/dev/drbdpool/rsc-1_00000\",\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you wanted to layer DRBD on top of this volume, which is the default `--layer-list` option in\n"
"LINSTOR for ZFS or LVM backed volumes, you would use the following resource creation pattern\n"
"instead:\n"
msgstr "もし、このボリューム上にDRBDをレイヤー化したい場合、ZFSやLVMでバックアップされたボリュームに対してLINSTORでのデフォルト`--layer-list`オプションはどうなるか疑問に思うことでしょう。その場合、以下のようなリソース作成パターンを使用します：\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-definition create rsc-1\n"
"# linstor volume-definition create rsc-1 100GiB\n"
"# linstor resource create --layer-list drbd,storage \\\n"
"          --storage-pool thin-lvm linstor-d rsc-1\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-definition create rsc-1\n"
"# linstor volume-definition create rsc-1 100GiB\n"
"# linstor resource create --layer-list drbd,storage \\\n"
"          --storage-pool thin-lvm linstor-d rsc-1\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "You would then see that you have a new Thin LVM backing a DRBD volume on `linstor-d`:\n"
msgstr "その後、`linstor-d` 上の新しい Thin LVM が DRBD ボリュームをバックアップしていることがわかります。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor --machine-readable resource list | grep -e device_path -e backing_disk\n"
"            \"device_path\": \"/dev/drbd1000\",\n"
"            \"backing_disk\": \"/dev/drbdpool/rsc-1_00000\",\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor --machine-readable resource list | grep -e device_path -e backing_disk\n"
"            \"device_path\": \"/dev/drbd1000\",\n"
"            \"backing_disk\": \"/dev/drbdpool/rsc-1_00000\",\n"

